data.description: Welcome to the Peake Homes "1725" floor-plan in Vancouver Meadows! Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 3 car garage all wrapped up nicely in 1,725 sq ft! This gorgeous home includes an 8 ft garage door, vaulted ceilings, oversized slider, covered patio, painted cabinets, 42" cabinets, 4 inch white trim, laminate flooring throughout entry, kitchen, living, and dining rooms with Quartz counter tops in the kitchen. Don't miss out on this one!
